reviews.review_text:
Matter of opinion Whether this source is inferior or not is completely a matter of opinion.  I for one think all the sources should be up here on LlaMA so people can decide for themselves which they like best.  That is, unless there are certain people who wish to set themselves up as supreme arbiter of others' tastes.

For myself, I think this is the best source here for this show.  It's the best balanced, enough Phil without saturating the other voices and instruments out of existence.  If Healy had had to patch out of a taper from whom to broadcast this show, I've no doubt it would have been this one.
My 14th show Good show, not an all-time fave, but pretty hot. I don't know if this is the recording I downloaded or not, but Cal Expo had great sound, so you basically can't go wrong.
